data.description: Check out this beautifully updated home on a little over an acre in Bridge City. Feel like you are out in the country while living in town. 2012 Sq ft of living space with an enclosed patio area and a large garage with a bathroom. 3 bedrooms 2 full baths with a really large dinning area. Plenty of extra room to park and store the boat, RV and all the toys. Recently updated outside with a new roof in 2021 and exterior paint and the interior throughout with new paint, and flooring. Located n a well established neighborhood at the end of two streets. The whole property is fenced with gated access to a long driveway. Call/Text for an appointment to see it in person.
